name: The more you cry stronger you get God too

metadata.description:
God art #00001

This was created by me and AI in the image of God's first weeping.
It is not only humans who become stronger the more they cry.
The gods have also shed many tears to become stronger.
In the future, we plan to work with various creators to create strong gods together!
metadata.name: The more you cry, stronger you get, God too
